    "ss_parallax_banner_CmyCXy": {
      "type": "ss-parallax-banner",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_cq8gje": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2>What happens when beauty stops being about <em>covering up.</em></h2>",
            "heading_custom": false,
            "heading_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
            "heading_size": 52,
            "heading_size_mobile": 30,
            "heading_height": 130,
            "heading_mt": 0,
            "heading_color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "text_bL6tVn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Hormones, aging, menopause, postpartum, stress, GLP-1 medications—</strong> so many things can cause lash and brow thinning. And for most people, nobody ever tells them that a solution even exists.</p><p></p><p>GrandeLASH-MD was born from that frustration. A once-nightly ritual—one swipe along the lash line—that supports visibly longer, fuller-looking lashes over time. No extensions. No faking it. Just your own lashes, at their best.</p><p>The Lash & Brow Confidence Project is our proof. <strong>25 real people. Unfiltered. Unscripted.</strong> We followed their frustrations, their skepticism, and—for most—their genuine surprise at what happened next.</p>",
            "text_custom": true,
            "text_font": "quattrocento_sans_n4",
            "text_size": 18,
            "text_size_mobile": 16,
            "text_height": 150,
            "text_mt": 38,
            "text_color": "#121212"
          }
        }
